import React from 'react';
import { Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom';
import Layout from '../components/Layout'; // Layout with header and footer
import HomePage from '../pages/HomePage'; // Main home page
import RestaurantHome from '../pages/RestaurantHome'; // Restaurant dashboard
import AdminHome from '../pages/AdminHome'; // Admin dashboard
import DeliveryPartnerHome from '../pages/DeliveryPartnerHome'; // Delivery partner dashboard
import Login from '../pages/Login'; // Login page
import Signup from '../pages/Signup'; // Signup page

function AppRoutes() {
  return (
    <Routes>
      
      <Route path="/" element={<Layout />}>
        
        <Route index element={<Mai/>} />
        
        
        <Route path="restauranthome" element={<RestaurantHome />}>
          <Route path="login" element={<Login />} />
          <Route path="signup" element={<Signup />} />
        </Route>
        
        <Route path="adminhome" element={<AdminHome />}>
          <Route path="login" element={<Login />} />
          <Route path="signup" element={<Signup />} />
        </Route>
        
        <Route path="deliverypartnerhome" element={<DeliveryPartnerHome />}>
          <Route path="login" element={<Login />} />
          <Route path="signup" element={<Signup />} />
        </Route>
      </Route>
    </Routes>
  );
}

export default AppRoutes;
